      "title": "President says state of emergency will not be extended",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe says that the State of Emergency, which is scheduled to lapse by the end of this week, will not be extended.",
        "\u201cAs the country\u2019s situation is back to normal, I will not extend the State of Emergency which is scheduled to lapse by the end of this week,\u201d he said today (16)."
      ],
